                                                            "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                            "actorId2": null,
                                                            "text": "<i>The Teachings of Ermahgerd, Goddess of Disbelief</i>. \"Ermagherd\"? I like her name. \"By Ermahgerd!\" \"Ermahgerddammit!\" \"Oh, my Ermagherd!\" I'm enjoying this!",
