                                            "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                            "actorId2": null,
                                            "text": "It's a complete bound collection, every single issue, of <i>Necronomicon Monthly</i>. You know, the magazine they put out before they published the book? The book was originally called <i>The Best from Necronomicon Magazine</i>, then they renamed it something shorter to make it catchy.",
