                                            "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                            "actorId2": null,
                                            "text": "From the back cover: \"The most fun you'll ever have reading about the joyful depravity described and permitted by our sacred texts.\" It's called <i>Children of a Lecher God</i>. Ermahgerd!",
